metadata.name: Twin Pagodas
metadata.description:
Twin Pagodas @ Doi Inthanon National Park, Thailand.
Thailand Treasure is a limited collection of unique digital art paintings.
The paintings are created from real-life pictures photographed and art edited by xNFTartist.
xNFTartist will aquire land in metaverse projects, and will do collabs with a few other exclusive NFT Projects.
The Thailand Treasure NFT will be your unique key to exclusive access and rewards.
Follow us for more updates...
